Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy governs the collection, use, and disclosure of information for the Flash Card mobile application.

1. Information We Collect
We only collect the following personal information directly from you:

Email Address: Used as your unique identifier for account creation and login.

Password: Securely stored for the purpose of account authentication.

We do not collect any other personal data, such as your name, location, or device identifiers. We do not use any third-party analytics or advertising services that collect your data.

2. How We Use Your Information
The information we collect is used solely for the following purposes:

Account Security: Your email and password are used to create and secure your user account, ensuring that only you have access to your created content.

Core App Functionality: Your account is necessary to enable the app's core features. This includes allowing teachers to securely create and organize educational content (questions, folders, subfolders) and enabling students to access and practice this content through the flash card and quiz methods.

3. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information you provide to us from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. Your password is encrypted before it is stored on our servers.

4. Data Retention
We will retain your information for as long as your account is active. If you wish to delete your account, please contact us using the information provided below. Upon deletion, your data will be permanently removed from our servers.

5. Your Rights
You have the right to access and correct your personal information. If you have any questions about the data we hold or wish to make changes, please contact us.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at:

Email: sayyid.ishaque@gmail.com
